    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<p>The Textarea field provides a multi-line text input for longer content with formatting options and character limits.</p>\n<h2>Key Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Multi-line text input</li>\n<li>Character counting</li>\n<li>Rows configuration</li>\n<li>New line handling</li>\n<li>Placeholder support</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Settings</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Default Value &#8211; Preset content</li>\n<li>Placeholder &#8211; Helper text</li>\n<li>Character Limit &#8211; Max length</li>\n<li>Rows &#8211; Input height</li>\n<li>New Lines &#8211; Handling options</li>\n</ul>\n",
